The Telegraph - Calcutta

 Jeff Crowe Match Referee

Thiruvananthapuram: Jeff Crowe will be the ICC Match Referee for the India versus South Africa Test series, BCCI secretary S.K. Nair said in a press release on Friday. 

Simon Taufel and Darrel Harper would be the umpires for the two-match Test series to be played in Kanpur from November 20 to 24 and in Calcutta from November 28 to December 2, the release added. 

Meanwhile, Taufel and K. Hariharan would be the umpires while I. Sivaram and Rajan K. Seth would be reserve umpires for the November 13 ODI in Calcutta, to celebrate the BCCI?s platinum jubilee. Clive Lloyd will act as the ICC Match Referee for the one-dayer. (PTI) 

